{"id":247373,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/维权网-南通维权人士周叶被关黑监狱14天再遭拘留/","date":"2012-08-16T13:46:08Z","modified":"2012-08-16T13:46:08Z","title":"维权网 | 南通维权人士周叶被关黑监狱14天再遭拘留（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张宁宁报道）南通拆迁维权人士周叶因揭发南通当局支持或者怂恿拆迁方逼迫拆迁户签订空白协议而受到南通当局的报复和陷害，将她关进黑监狱，又关进拘留所。但周叶勇敢地揭露南通拆迁空白协议和阴阳协议，却得到南通拆迁户的赞许，当周叶从拘留所释放时获得众多拆迁受害人的欢迎，竟震动了南通当局。当局派出大批警察将迎接周叶回家的维权人士一一拘押至下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>点后才释放。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>点左右，周叶等拆迁受害人到国家监察部上访，被南通市截访人员截访，强行将周叶等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>位南通拆迁受害人塞进一辆依维柯汽车（车牌：京</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">e36369 </span><span>），押送到回南通，把周叶的随身物品、手机等没收。周叶被南通当局关押在南通市北阁饭店达</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>南通市北阁饭店是臭名昭著的黑监狱，关过无数冤民。南通当局将周叶关进黑监狱还不过瘾，又对她作出行政拘留处罚</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>天的处罚。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，周叶在被关黑监狱期间，当局时常不给周叶喝水，甚至不许她上厕所，还不准周叶睡觉，百般折磨她。连续对周叶询问</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>次，做了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>次询问笔录。周叶在黑监狱内拒绝签字。于是，将周叶送拘留所关押</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>天。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>但这一切迫害并没有使周叶屈服，获得自由后的周叶表示将提起行政诉讼，揭露黑监狱和对她的非法羁押。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-UOaZmyxrgO0/UCzznfuAfgI/AAAAAAAALac/-SwpwandhPY/s1600/%E5%8D%97%E9%80%9A%E9%BB%91%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"202\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-UOaZmyxrgO0/UCzznfuAfgI/AAAAAAAALac/-SwpwandhPY/s320/%E5%8D%97%E9%80%9A%E9%BB%91%E7%9B%91%E7%8B%B1.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>南通黑监狱</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-xqNcdw9XzYk/UCzzwUbXJKI/AAAAAAAALak/-jdvXBVC2Hg/s1600/%E5%91%A8%E5%8F%B6.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-xqNcdw9XzYk/UCzzwUbXJKI/AAAAAAAALak/-jdvXBVC2Hg/s320/%E5%91%A8%E5%8F%B6.jpg\" width=\"226\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-QYnmYi4uGxE/UCzzz2jhPXI/AAAAAAAALas/jNXvqRMQ2Kw/s1600/%E5%91%A8%E5%8F%B6%E5%A4%84%E7%BD%9A%E4%B9%A6.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-QYnmYi4uGxE/UCzzz2jhPXI/AAAAAAAALas/jNXvqRMQ2Kw/s320/%E5%91%A8%E5%8F%B6%E5%A4%84%E7%BD%9A%E4%B9%A6.jpg\" width=\"226\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-cOJrN1cz8DU/UCzz3Hagh_I/AAAAAAAALa0/DvBfjtGzOPU/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-cOJrN1cz8DU/UCzz3Hagh_I/AAAAAAAALa0/DvBfjtGzOPU/s320/1.jpg\" width=\"222\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">      </span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-892932494609968816?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}